information: The company ALBERT HANDTMANN METALLGUSSWERK GMBH & CO. KG, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 1872, which operates in the Steel industry. It also operates in the Iron, special grade and pig iron, Aluminium and aluminium alloys, Foundries, aluminium, and Steels and metals - machining industries. It is based in Biberach, Germany.
